  Locus:
    Page: 407
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Search
---
Withdraw into yourself and look. And if you do not find yourself beautiful
as yet, do as the creator of a statue that is to be made beautiful; he cuts
away here, he smoothes there, he makes this line lighter, this other purer,
until he has shown a beautiful face upon the statue.
